ver 0.10 no stable release will be released, always a beta
GPL Licensed, (c) 2011 Muhammad Najmi Ahmad Zabidi <najmi.zabidi AT gmail.com>
To work beautifully, use with Ubuntu Font, need to be installed/fetched from
https://github.com/tzwenn/ubuntu-latex-fonts/branches

This is distributed AS IS, I will not be responsible for any disaster caused by this .sty package
It should work.. nothing harm

Create your local customize directory
unzip the zip file
cd the zipfile
mkdir -p $HOME/texmf/tex/latex/beamer/base/themes/theme
mkdir -p $HOME/texmf/tex/latex/beamer/base/themes/color
cp -v beamercolorthemeampangcolor.sty  $HOME/texmf/tex/latex/beamer/base/themes/color
cp -v beamerthemeAmpang.sty $HOME/texmf/tex/latex/beamer/base/themes/theme

To invoke, put in the preamble of your beamer file:

\usetheme{Ampang}
\usecolortheme{ampangcolor}


 
